Package com.Akif

Class MyDeque<E>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
com.Akif.MyDeque<E>
Type Parameters:
E - Type of the list
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.util.Queue<E>
public class MyDeque<E>
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
implements java.util.Deque<E>
This class is implementation of Deque class which implements Deque interface and extends from AbstractCollection Class . It uses DoubleLinkedList class references to keep data.
See Also:
DoubleLinkedList
